---
// Definition section — mirrors README "What Roady is, and is not" table.
// Source of truth: docs/positioning.md.
---

<section class="py-16 border-t border-white/5 bg-[#0D1117]">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
    <p class="text-center text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-violet-400 font-semibold mb-3">
      Built narrowly, on purpose
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-center text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-12">
      What Roady is, and is not
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center">
          <i data-lucide="check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400 mr-2"></i>
          Roady is&hellip;
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-400">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-violet-400 mr-2">&bull;</span>
            The plan-of-record for an AI-paired feature
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-violet-400 mr-2">&bull;</span>
            Memory that survives <code class="mono text-gray-300">/clear</code> and session resets
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-violet-400 mr-2">&bull;</span>
            File-based, git-friendly, local-first
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-violet-400 mr-2">&bull;</span>
            MCP-native &mdash; every operation is a tool
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-violet-400 mr-2">&bull;</span>
            Drift detection between intent, plan, and code
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center">
          <i data-lucide="x-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400 mr-2"></i>
          Roady is not&hellip;
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-400">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-red-400/50 mr-2">&bull;</span>
            A Jira / Linear replacement
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-red-400/50 mr-2">&bull;</span>
            A chat history layer
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-red-400/50 mr-2">&bull;</span>
            A hosted SaaS (today &mdash; see <a href="https://github.com/felixgeelhaar/roady/blob/main/ROADMAP.md" class="text-violet-400 underline">ROADMAP</a>)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-red-400/50 mr-2">&bull;</span>
            A code-search or context-stuffing tool
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
